org.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM spree_variants INNER JOIN spree_products ON spree_products.id = spree_variants.product_id WHERE spree_variants.deleted_at IS NULL AND (LOWER(spree_products.name) LIKE LOWER('%variant_white%') OR LOWER(sku) LIKE LOWER('%variant_white%'))

rewrites.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM spree_variants INNER JOIN spree_products ON spree_products.id = spree_variants.product_id WHERE spree_variants.deleted_at IS NULL AND (LOWER(spree_products.name) LIKE LOWER('%variant_white%') OR LOWER(sku) LIKE LOWER('%variant_white%')) LIMIT 1
